snippet.title: ぼっち・ざ・ろっく!  (Bocchi the Rock!) - Heaven For Death - Part 1 Playthrough
snippet.description:
Cute little Bocchi the Rock yuri visual novel.
Ryou is dead and amnesiac and Nijika is her angel. Together they're in heaven.
Original game by S_RefriGE
ENG TL by YuriKnights
Download the TL here!
